data.description: Incredible 360 Mountain views located in superior! Extra large lot over 15,000sqft.  This 1991 MFG home features over 1400 sqft, 4 bedrooms 2 bathrooms, Kitchen recently upgraded, new appliances, 4 ton AC!  Step inside to large living room, vaulted ceilings, oversized bedrooms. Plenty of opportunity to customize this home to suit your needs.  Three outbuildings for extra storage, property is completely fenced in (chain link).  Dont miss out on the chance to own this remarkable property with stunning views!
